\section*{streamit-2.0}

\begin{itemize}

\item Snapshot release of internal infrastructure (August 2005).  This
snapshot has new features, bug fixes, and also new bugs compared to
the initial public release.  Major features are as follows, please
contact us if you have any questions:

\begin{itemize}
\item Faster and more memory-efficient Java library (up to 10X).
\item Faster uniprocessor implementation (up to 2X).
\item Snapshot of current cache optimizations.
\item Snapshot of current cluster backend.
\item JPEG decoder/encoder application (supported in library only).
\item Limited support for dynamic rates and messaging in Java library.
\end{itemize}

\item Initial public release (October 2003).
\end{itemize}

